title: koha sql acquisition grouped by aq budget between date range
content:
SELECT aqb.budget_name, COUNT(b.biblioitemnumber)
FROM biblioitems b 
LEFT JOIN aqorders aq on
(b.biblionumber=aq.biblionumber)
left JOIN aqbudgets aqb on
(aq.budget_id=aqb.budget_id)
LEFT JOIN items i on
(i.biblionumber=aq.biblionumber)

WHERE
   date(i.dateaccessioned) BETWEEN  <<–û—Ç|date>>  AND  <<–î–æ|date>> 
GROUP BY aqb.budget_name 
ORDER BY COUNT(b.biblionumber) desc
